subsection.def:
goods
                    (貨品) has the same meaning as in the Sale of
                Goods Ordinance (Cap. 26);

notice
                    (告示) includes an announcement, whether or not
                in writing, and any other communication or pretended communication;

paragraph.content:
any contract so far as it relates to the creation or transfer of an
                    interest in land, or to the termination of such an interest, whether by
                    extinction, merger, surrender, forfeiture or otherwise;

subparagraph.content:
to the formation or dissolution of a company (which means any body
                        corporate or unincorporated association and includes a partnership);
                        or
